# Testing and Validation Gate

- For CRUD feature changes, maintain baseline coverage across:
  - mapper behavior
  - store behavior
  - page/component interaction
- Add or update specs when introducing new shared components or new UI interaction patterns.
- After substantive edits, run:
  - `bun ng build`
  - `bun ng test --watch=false`
- Do not consider work complete when introduced tests fail.
- Keep tests focused on behavior and contracts, not implementation details.
